火爆游戏《Palworld》正在VTuber们陆续发行中。 https://p2y.jp/smash-hit-game-palworld-is-being-streamed-by-vtuber-one-after-another/ https://p2y.jp/smash-hit-game-palworld-is-being-streamed-by-vtuber-one-after-another/#respondp2y_admin Sun, 21 Jan 2024 08:39:02 +0000 PCVTuberゲームバーチャルNeo-PorteSteamTwitterXbox Game PassXbox Series SXbox Series XYouTubeななしいんくぶいすぽっ！オープンワールドパルワールド(Palworld)ホロライブプロダクションポケットペア https://p2y.jp/?p=112617 <p> Pocket Pair 推出的 Xbox Series X/S/Steam（PC）抢先体验版游戏软件“Palworld”大受欢迎。 VTuber酱[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/smash-hit-game-palworld-is-being-streamed-by-vtuber-one-after-another/">VTuber发行的重磅游戏《Palworld》已陆续开始</a>首发于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; <p></p><p> Pocket Pair 推出的 Xbox Series X/S/Steam（PC）抢先体验版游戏软件《 <strong>Palworld</strong> 》大受欢迎。据确认，VTuber艺人的作品分发已陆续开始。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1100" height="619" data-attachment-id="112637" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/smash-hit-game-palworld-is-being-streamed-by-vtuber-one-after-another/smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/smash_hit_game_palworld_is_being_streamed_by_vtuber_one_after_another.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-112637" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源： <a href="https://youtu.be/j20R83J_U2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="YouTube">YouTube</a><br> © Pocketpair, Inc.<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p>《Palworld》是一款由Pocket Pair开发并发行的开放世界生存游戏。以名为“Pal”的生物居住的世界为背景，您可以与最多 32 人一起享受在线游戏。</p><p> Xbox Series X/S 和 Steam 的抢先体验版将于 1 月 19 日发布。发行后8小时销量100万张，24小时销量200万张，40小时销量300万张，大受欢迎。 1月21日16:00，Steam上同时玩家数突破100万，成为Steam历史上全球播放量最多的日本游戏。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/charts/mostplayed" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="最常玩的游戏">最常玩的游戏</a></p><cite>蒸汽</cite></blockquote><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%91%E3%83%AB%E3%83%AF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB%E3%83%89?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Palworld</a>发布后 40 小时内销量突破三百万！<br><br>非常感谢你和这么多人一起玩！<br><br>这将是对开发团队的鼓励，所以如果您觉得有趣，请留下“推荐”评论来支持我们！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B1%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%E3%83%9A%E3%82%A2?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PocketPairpic.twitter.com</a> <a href="https://t.co/9zPL4HEX5w">/9zPL4HEX5w</a></p> — Palworld/Palworld 官方 (@Palworld_JP) <a href="https://twitter.com/Palworld_JP/status/1748871528467648812?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 21 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider